==========================================
README for the SystemC 2.3.1 documentation
==========================================

This directory contains

doxygen/ 

  A folder containing a command file (template) for doxygen which may be
  used to generate browseable documentation of the SystemC class library.
  Please see www.doxygen.org for usage.

archived/

  Documentation from earlier versions of SystemC, much of which is now
  out-of-date.  Please consult the IEEE Std. 1666-2011 for normative
  SystemC documentation.

SystemC_2011_New_Features.pdf

  A presentation outlining the new features of IEEE 1666-2011,
  first given at DVCON (Design and Verification Conference)
  in February 2012.

README - this file.
